Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道自己在幹什麼嗎

Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫慰的帝國

Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特隊隊長亞伯力克·基烈特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來報道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於嘉依卡 我隊除當初追捕的一名外又增加一名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下正追蹤兩名嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他隊有什麼新情報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前沒什麼實質上的進展
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機關長 我想再看一下賈茲皇帝的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些及其他從賈茲城收押的東西都保管在書庫裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 事到如今還有什麼好查的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞伯力克 這五年來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們對嘉依卡的案件一直很重視
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但關於皇帝的詳細情況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話即便如今我們已經擊殺了他 仍然對他不夠了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡收集遺體的行為真會對我們造成威脅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個嘉依卡從我眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪走了阿巴爾特伯爵擁有的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的目的與「威脅」相差甚遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 祭悼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括有裝鎧龍與他們一同行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確有些地方令人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我實在看不出他們有顛覆國家的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是有些別的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞伯力克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從嘉依卡的案件抽手一段時間怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡的問題確實是很重要的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但目前 我們的首要職責
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是實際改善大陸人民的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須以這為最優先
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振動大 操縱 難關
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們特地選了條小路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這根本稱不上是路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個將你和機車連接起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並通過魔法思念料驅動它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與機杖 同樣構造
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化石 礦石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體中所含生物的記憶 思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部 魔法的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法的思念料 一切魔法之源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈茲皇帝的遺體也是很強大的魔法思念料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長 你知道現今大部分魔法技術是誰發明的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是賈茲皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這機車和機杖 都是你爸發明的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 偉大的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關卡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請交通行費
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是新賈茲帝國的領土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0110,0040,,{\fs38}NeoGaz
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得賈茲帝國 自從五年前皇帝被殺就滅亡了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是渴望復興帝國之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現正與去世皇帝的遺孤 嘉依卡公主一同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此地建立新的帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡公主?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚愕的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是將軍馬拉德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及大臣拉布魯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我是近衛隊隊長弗洛魯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊那位就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新賈茲帝國的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡公主是也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 嘉依卡喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無禮 要向嘉依卡公主多表敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且把通行費交了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行許可 申請
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟拿銀幣出來 你腦子裡在想些什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一看你們很是可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我們還得趕路…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要檢查一下車內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是道具箱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是這城來那鎮去的候鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在這個村子 明天在那個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給大家帶去幸福的江湖賣藝人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江湖賣藝人?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 也為了證明你們的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來給嘉依卡公主表演些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我很想看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是新賈茲城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這個?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不准何時又會有六國聯盟的追兵前來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此這只是為瞞過世人眼睛的暫時的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以這裡的皇帝之女嘉依卡公主為旗首
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以新賈茲帝國的復活為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫離開國家的賈茲帝國國民們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬眾一心集結在了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再者還另有對六國聯盟心懷不滿的有志之士們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在支持我們的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國復興之日已近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天讓大家欣賞幾項我們的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由於本事還未到家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有失誤 還請多多包涵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取出的這個蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神奇 扔出去也不會落地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 怎麼樣 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是這邊的蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神奇 它會把飛向少女的匕首都吸過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像在哪兒見過?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是這隻小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是隻只要施展咒語 就會顯露出本性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乎其神的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:07:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏拉 烏拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏拉 烏拉 烏拉 烏拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏拉拉 烏拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了 那女孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什麼來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全神貫注中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…這事不要太鑽牛角尖比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人在等我?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於賈茲皇帝有弄明白什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說沒什麼有價值的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連他出生相關的情報都不明不白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以為至少應該會有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝到死前一直著手的最前沿技術的資料的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼關於嘉依卡的事情呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只聽說有殘黨想擁立嘉依卡企圖復興帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有實際確認到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人 今天的用餐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我今天從早上到現在還什麼都沒吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起去吃個飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好棒的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街頭藝人體力很重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃多點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在棺材裡放隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果一打開變成了裝鎧龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個戲法 到底是怎麼辦到的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微透露一點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛魯 你喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡所有人 賈茲帝國國民?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你們也是賈茲帝國出身?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼不早說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.37,0:10:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我馬上拿去換成軍資金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了喔 同志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了賈茲帝國的復興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重振皇室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新賈茲帝國萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗屁新賈茲帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說白了不就是一群盜賊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已經吃足一枚銀幣的飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要繼續待下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 名字叫做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡和托魯是什麼關係?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的表演 兩人配合好默契啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是兄妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡他?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定 堅決否定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新賈茲帝國 復興 希望?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想給因戰爭而流離失所的賈茲帝國國民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供一處棲身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 我想重建帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有棲身之所 幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的 大家的幸福?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 芙蕾多妮卡也是賈茲人吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能不能一起來幫忙復興帝國?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫忙?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起去拜訪資產家的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請他們給予資金援助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要芙蕾多妮卡開口請求他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家都會慷慨解囊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫幫我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法忘懷的 有你的冬天的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等候 你那身影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比凍結的吐息更清白的肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比大地更清澈的藍色眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞麻色的頭髮如琥珀般閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情詩?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這是賈茲帝國的詩人的詩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想記下來嗎 我教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:13:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 你那如陽光般的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將顫抖的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡公主 請移駕執務室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天再繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 約定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩兒是個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再加把勁就能攻陷她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外兩人交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少把錢全弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那機車也一定不能放過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人有約不能走?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續和那幫傢伙糾纏可沒好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點趕路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯正確
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我 約定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那約定有這麼重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會被那套新賈茲帝國建國的說辭騙到了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是收集父親遺體吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定 接著反駁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚出發 明早出發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差別無大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路況很差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明早再走較為明智
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且沒嘉依卡開車 機車也動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再出發也無妨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性 道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是心太軟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉布魯負責食堂的銀餐具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿貯藏庫裡的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量挑些值錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陷阱 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是舊賈茲帝國的國民吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有意與我們一起復興賈茲帝國嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做江湖藝人 四處漂泊也很辛苦吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據你們的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證給你們相應的地位喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉失敗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是普通的江湖藝人吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才發現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見過通緝令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡帶著棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一頭銀色頭髮 有一對紫色眼瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:15:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要借嘉依卡這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起碼先調查清楚再借啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不早說啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是曾經想說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們剛才胡扯什麼復興賈茲帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實就是想也捲走我們的錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計你的同伴也都是這樣騙入夥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本沒想騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初我們是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 目標太過遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是維持每日的生計就已經精疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是被生活所迫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們也沒有完全放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日會將帝國…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬拉德 出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉婭她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我們穿幫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉婭怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 那是個陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們徹底中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我問你尤莉婭去哪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊的牢房裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到沒 明白了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不願再添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就此告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯還是挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 尤莉婭 救出 請求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫再牽扯較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉婭 約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢房在地下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能帶人從那裡逃出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不可能的 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法使用 救出可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 努力 尤莉婭 救出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:17:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯現吧 沉默不語者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Silencer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正被六國聯盟追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已才藏身此處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你出去 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 你們不是來救我了麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我們道聲謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂 要謝就謝嘉依卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝搭救之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔地包裹著顫抖的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以春天的光輝填滿我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈茲的冬景
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的你就是春天的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永不忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的對不起 我欺騙了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡為什麼旅行?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 祭悼 為了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你目標早日實現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝福 感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是時候做個轉變了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後的路又該怎麼走…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標 再尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物歸原主我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能問件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈茲皇帝是什麼樣的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如人品之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算問我 我連他長什麼樣都沒見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只聽大家都說是個了不得的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們住在鄉下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不清楚皇帝的事情 日子也是照樣過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連那個他為了研發魔法技術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行了非常可疑的人體實驗的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是戰後才聽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 實際情況我們一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還問這個做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是隨便問問
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們今後打算怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直拖延下來的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候付諸行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連賈茲帝國的國民
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不清楚皇帝的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老爸真是充滿謎團啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 他們今後打算怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再發現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標 再發現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是很嚴重的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.15,0:21:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派往加瓦爾尼公爵領
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求返還航天要塞索厄拉的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟被殺害 變成淒慘的屍體回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須立即進行武力制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法思念料 枯竭在即
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採購 必須
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 今天 終戰紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店舖皆休息 我為難
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.41,0:23:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周 第九集 「記憶的價值」

